snippet.title: ModeMarvelous
snippet.description:
Welcome to ModeMarvelous - the home of exclusive CONCEPT trailers for (mostly) Marvel characters. 

It's a showcase for all manner of fan art, fan theories and trailer themes... Underrated characters? Overrated heroes?? Imaginary heroes??? You'll find them all here!

Header art by @elilusionista.cl

Email for business enquiries or collaboration:
▸ modemarvelous@gmail.com

▸ The purpose of these videos is to use brief clippings of existing media to communicate a new concept/idea that fans are able to consume as either celebratory or theoretical commentary on how a film/cinematic universe could look. This is often intended as parody and/or social critique on the typical male hero-trope either by providing light on female heroism in its place or by mimicking action trailer themes. It draws upon existing art to suggest new ventures and/or propose changes to current products.
